  <h2 id="best-practices">Best practices</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Use <code>CardImage</code> with a descriptive <code>alt</code> for accessibility</li>
    <li>Limit <code>CardDescription</code> content with <code>truncate</code> to keep a consistent design</li>
    <li>Use <code>elevation</code> to create visual hierarchy between cards</li>
    <li>Enable <code>interactive</code> only for clickable cards</li>
    <li>Group metadata with <code>CardMeta</code> for better readability</li>
    <li>Use <code>CardFooter</code> for main actions related to the card</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>The component uses the semantic <code>&lt;article&gt;</code> tag</li>
    <li>Images require an <code>alt</code> attribute</li>
    <li>Headers use <code>&lt;header&gt;</code> and footers use <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></li>
    <li>Interactive mode adds visible focus states</li>
    <li>Metadata is structured in a <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> list</li>
  </ul>
